title: im taking requests ?
body:
hello im bored AS HELL and everytime i do this no one ends up sending me a request anyway but lets do this anyway !

click here to send me a scenario n a bts or stray kids member, anything you like (no smut though) or use one of these shitty prompts from a list i’ve had saved since i was like 14

prompt list:

1. “I should go.” “Or you could stay a little longer.”
2. “You really think that?”
3. “Sorry, was I interrupting something?“
4. “Please remember that I love you.”
5. “Tipsy isn’t the same as drunk.”
6. “I need a favour….”
7. “Wow, I am so in love with you… just wow.”
8. “I can’t trust you anymore.”
9. "I can’t believe I actually ever trusted you.”
10. “I don’t know how to love someone without hurting them.”
11. “I’m fine, stop asking me that.”
12. “I didn’t mean to hurt/upset you.”
13. “Me? Jealous?”
14. “Delete that now.”
15. “I swear if you hit me with your pillow one more time.”
16. “Don’t leave me!”
17. “Say something!”
18. “You’re so cute when you’re stubborn.”
19. “You think I’m adorable?”
20. “You’re allowed to be happy, you know that right?”
21. “We’re in the middle of nowhere!”
22. “You take the bed, you need it more than me.”
23. “You’re ridiculous”
24. “You’re so warm!”
25. “You’re freezing, jesus!”
26. “I’m sorry….”
27. “Stop saying sorry!”
28. “You owe me one”
29. “You always look beautiful.”
30. “Do you need anything?”
31. “Hold on. You’re telling me that you want to go out to the creepy woods in the middle of the night? Really? Really?”
32. “Be quiet! You’ll get us caught!”
33. “How would you feel if it was you?”
34. “Sometimes I just want to cuddle, okay? Is that so bad?”
35. “Is that my shirt?”
36. “Now I know where half my wardrobe went.”
37. “Just..just smile and don’t talk too much”
38. “You’re really special to me.”
39. “You scared the shit out of me!”
40. “You haven’t been yourself.”
41. “It wasn’t that bad.”
42. “I think that’s enough wine for tonight.”
43. “Stop worrying.”
44. “You don’t have to pretend with me.”
45. “Maybe you should leave the cooking to me.”
46. “Try not to think about it.”
47. “None of this makes any sense.”
48. “Are you trying to get yourself killed?”
49. “Bad dream?”
50. “I love you, you mean the world to me.”

18. “You’re so cute when you’re stubborn.”
19. “You think I’m adorable?”
20. “You’re allowed to be happy, you know that right?”
21. “We’re in the middle of nowhere!”
22. “You take the bed, you need it more than me.”
23. “You’re ridiculous”
24. “You’re so warm!”
25. “You’re freezing, jesus!”
26. “I’m sorry….”
27. “Stop saying sorry!”
28. “You owe me one”
29. “You always look beautiful.”
30. “Do you need anything?”
31. “Hold on. You’re telling me that you want to go out to the creepy woods in the middle of the night? Really? Really?”
32. “Be quiet! You’ll get us caught!”
33. “How would you feel if it was you?”
34. “Sometimes I just want to cuddle, okay? Is that so bad?”
35. “Is that my shirt?”
36. “Now I know where half my wardrobe went.”
37. “Just..just smile and don’t talk too much”
38. “You’re really special to me.”
39. “You scared the shit out of me!”
40. “You haven’t been yourself.”
41. “It wasn’t that bad.”
42. “I think that’s enough wine for tonight.”
43. “Stop worrying.”
44. “You don’t have to pretend with me.”
45. “Maybe you should leave the cooking to me.”
46. “Try not to think about it.”
47. “None of this makes any sense.”
48. “Are you trying to get yourself killed?”
49. “Bad dream?”
50. “I love you, you mean the world to me.”

body:
BTS reaction to meeting their S/O’s children from a past relationship

Jin


Seokjin would be quite nervous. He d want you child(ren) to like him and He’d do anything in his power to do so. You’d constantly have to reassure him that everything would be fine.


Suga


Yoongi would be a bit less but on the inside. He show you that he’s cool about it but really it’s nerve wrecking for him. He deeply hopes that they’ll like him. Eventually you’d find out he was a hot mess and try to soothe his worries.


J-Hope


Hoseok is through the roof happy more than he is worried. Every now and then he’ll ask a question about them, he’d do his best to prepare; find out about them, how they looked and so on. He was totally prepare until the day actually came then he’d just be a bundle of nerves


RM


Namjoon would be a bit awkward, not sure what to do but he’s try his best to get along with them. You know you can entrust Namjoon with your child(ren) but just not around a stove. Namjoon would be mostly fine, with a few nerves here and there.


Jimin


I have no idea what I’m going to do, this would be in Jimin’s mind constantly. Jimin would break out inside and outside. He’d push back the date that they were set to meet because he was so nervous. You’d have to push him and continuously comfort him.


V


Complete and utter excitement, Taehyung was ready for this day in fact he had you move the day up, although, he did feel a bit nervous he was overwhelmed with excitement overall.


Jungkook


Being very honest with you jungkook would say that he has no idea what to do. He would be the kind of awkward around your child(ren), it will take him quite a while to get used to them and vice versa

~A

Everything is still open

title: I am back.
body:
But I will be here to lurk only. 

I quit my job which I loved, but it stopped being fun when it hit the 6th month. I couldn’t transition to the next phase they wanted me to do, so I quit. Simple.

I have a solo exhibit this weekend and I am happy to say I am back to my old self. Still weary from my bad depressive state a couple of months ago, but compared to then, I am better now.

Still into TMNT, but now BTS (Bangtan Sonyeondan) has wormed its way into my heart. They were both the reason/s why I snapped out from my depressive state…but no, won’t be making fanart of those two…for now. Who knows. Ask me again in 3 months. 

Miss you all and thanks for reading.
